    <chapter title="删除" id="delete">
        <chapter title="带条件删除" id="deleteWhere">
            <tldr>
                <p>
                    API 参考：<a href="https://jetbrains.github.io/Exposed/api/exposed-jdbc/org.jetbrains.exposed.v1.jdbc/delete-where.html">
                    <code>deleteWhere</code> (JDBC)
                    </a>，<a href="https://jetbrains.github.io/Exposed/api/exposed-r2dbc/org.jetbrains.exposed.v1.r2dbc/delete-where.html">
                        <code>deleteWhere</code> (R2DBC)
                    </a>
                </p>
            </tldr>
            <p>
                要删除记录并返回删除的行数，请使用 <code>.deleteWhere()</code>
